\newlabel{fig:narr}{{9a}{14}{Narration mechanism (Claude).\relax }{figure.caption.11}{}}
\newlabel{sub@fig:narr}{{a}{14}{Narration mechanism (Claude).\relax }{figure.caption.11}{}}
\newlabel{fig:kfmodel}{{9b}{14}{Keyframe-image value, in context.\relax }{figure.caption.11}{}}
\newlabel{sub@fig:kfmodel}{{b}{14}{Keyframe-image value, in context.\relax }{figure.caption.11}{}}
\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {9}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {What narration and keyframes contribute.} \textbf  {(a)} Visual narration lifts Claude from 64\% (visual+ASR, no narration) to 82\%: discarding the narration text after it is generated keeps 74\%, splitting the $+18$\,pp into ${\sim }{+}10$\,pp inference-time articulation ($^\dagger $directional, $p{=}0.12$) and $+8$\,pp from persisting it as memory ($p{=}0.039$). \textbf  {(b)} The marginal value of the inter-step keyframe \emph  {images}, measured with audio and narration already present, is model-specific: $+10$/$+6$\,pp on Claude/Gemini\nobreakspace  {}2.5 (realised only through narration---just $+1$\,pp as raw input), neutral on GPT-5.4, and a $-12$\,pp \emph  {penalty} on Gemini\nobreakspace  {}3 (image-token dilution, Section\nobreakspace  {}\ref  {sec:why_g3}).\relax }}{14}{figure.caption.11}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:analysis}{{9}{14}{\textbf {What narration and keyframes contribute.} \textbf {(a)} Visual narration lifts Claude from 64\% (visual+ASR, no narration) to 82\%: discarding the narration text after it is generated keeps 74\%, splitting the $+18$\,pp into ${\sim }{+}10$\,pp inference-time articulation ($^\dagger $directional, $p{=}0.12$) and $+8$\,pp from persisting it as memory ($p{=}0.039$). \textbf {(b)} The marginal value of the inter-step keyframe \emph {images}, measured with audio and narration already present, is model-specific: $+10$/$+6$\,pp on Claude/Gemini~2.5 (realised only through narration---just $+1$\,pp as raw input), neutral on GPT-5.4, and a $-12$\,pp \emph {penalty} on Gemini~3 (image-token dilution, Section~\ref {sec:why_g3}).\relax }{figure.caption.11}{}}
